attributes.review: This app is so horrible. I wish I could give it 0 stars. The second I downloaded it all of my apps crashed and my phone immediately died. When my phone turned back on it was playing “be happy” at full volume and I couldn’t turn it off. The song wasn’t playing from iTunes or Spotify, but it was coming directly from the app. I couldn’t open the app to turn it off and I couldn’t close out of it. This is an absolute scam and a promotional ploy for the song. After a while it gets kind of catchy, but DO NOT DOWNLOAD THIS APP. It doesn’t belong on the App Store at all.
